name: Hybrid
tagline: The all in one shell script!
body:
Features:
- Cache dropper
- Rubbish cleaner
- DB Optimizer
- VM, LMK & TCP Optimizations
- Logger removal
- Basic kernel control
- Ninite for Android (No affiliation with official ninite)
- Game Booster

Changes:
- v1.0 - Initial public release
- v1.1 - Added installation support to more functions
- v1.2 - Added game booster
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
